  "texts": [
    "Genomics experts heavily rely on data visualization for the sensemaking of complex data.",
    "The importance of visualization in the sensemaking process is apparent in the wide variety of visualization tools for genomics data analysis [52].",
    "Typically, these tools provide off-the-shelf solutions tailored to support analysis tasks.",
    "Because of the highly collaborative nature and the diversity of questions to be addressed, genomics experts also engage in visualization authoring activities.",
    "These activities include the design and implementation of data visualizations, both for the goal of data exploration and communication of data insights."
  ],
